attributionInfo.brokerName: THE REAL ESTATE CENTER OF NEW BERN, INC

data.description: Charming ranch-style retreat in the heart of New Bern that you can be in by the New Year! SELLER IS OFFERING A 2,000 USE AS YOU CHOOSE CREDIT FOR THE BUYERS. This spacious 2200 sqft home offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality, situated on a generous .67-acre lot. As you approach, you'll appreciate the convenience of a two-car covered carport, providing shelter for your vehicles. Step inside, and a welcoming entryway leads you to a sprawling living area and kitchen. To your right, a versatile space awaits, perfect for use as an office, sitting area, and dining room. The living area boasts plush carpeting and elegant trey ceilings, creating an inviting atmosphere seamlessly connecting to the kitchen which enhances the open layout. The kitchen itself is a culinary dream, featuring a breakfast bar, durable LVP flooring, pristine white cabinets, stainless steel appliance. Enjoy the view of the expansive backyard as you prepare meals and entertain guests. Your primary bedroom is a true retreat, offering plush carpeting, his and her walk-in closets, and an ensuite bathroom for added privacy and luxury. Two additional bedrooms with cozy carpeting and reach-in closets share a well-appointed full-sized bathroom. An extra flex room with LVP flooring, accessible from the carport, adds versatility to the home, serving as a mudroom, office, or additional storage space. The large walk-in laundry room, complete with built-in shelving and a utility sink, provides practicality and convenience, with easy access to the backyard. Out back you will find a large yard backing up to mature trees giving you privacy. The fenced-in area with a raised garden bed beckons to those with a green thumb. NO CITY TAXES! Conveniently located in James City. less than 10 minutes to Downtown New Bern, a short drive to MCAS Cherry Point, and less than an hour to Crystal Coast Beaches!
